---
title: All-American Beef & Caramelised Onion Pie with Cheesy Potato Topping & Cucumber Salad
description: This cosy dinner packs a smokey, veggie-loaded beef base full of flavour, then tops off the whole dish with decadent and
delicious gooey Cheddar mashed potatoes. Finishing the meal off under the grill ensures you're eating your tasty creation
as fast as possible!
